    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Creating arrays\n",
        "\n",
        "### Arrays created from lists and other array-like objects\n"
      ],
      "id": "6a422648"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "f5f05ea2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array(((1, 2), (3, 4)))\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "c6d8ee70",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with constant values\n"
      ],
      "id": "3ffea844"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.zeros((2, 3))"
      ],
      "id": "d524d1bb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.ones(4)\n",
        "data, data.dtype"
      ],
      "id": "6dcf26cd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "5.4 * np.ones(10)"
      ],
      "id": "4b4e4897",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.full(10, 5.4) # slightly more efficient"
      ],
      "id": "50945724",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x1 = np.empty(5)\n",
        "x1.fill(3.0)\n",
        "x1"
      ],
      "id": "e7ee06da",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with incremental sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "5557a60e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.arange(0, 11, 1)"
      ],
      "id": "89e291b2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.linspace(0, 10, 11)  # generally recommended"
      ],
      "id": "c561bc2c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with logarithmic sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "00327a07"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.logspace(0, 2, 10)  # 5 data points between 10**0=1 to 10**2=100"
      ],
      "id": "dd7109ff",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Mesh grid arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "f1894905"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([-1, 0, 1])\n",
        "y = np.array([-2, 0, 2])\n",
        "\n",
        "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "edceca88",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "X"
      ],
      "id": "3a45fa80",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Y"
      ],
      "id": "542add9c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Z = (X + Y)**2\n",
        "Z"
      ],
      "id": "3348fbf9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating uninitialized arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "1eb97fd5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.empty(3, dtype=float)"
      ],
      "id": "9b9efe25",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating arrays with properties of other arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "912ef4fe"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def f(x):    \n",
        "    y = np.ones_like(x)    # compute with x and y    \n",
        "    return y\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]])\n",
        "y = f(x)\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "a810d36f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating matrix arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "2905f4a5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.identity(4)"
      ],
      "id": "10dfad13",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=1)"
      ],
      "id": "efe6f1ae",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=-1)"
      ],
      "id": "af96edae",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.diag(np.arange(0, 20, 5))"
      ],
      "id": "783a5065",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Indexing and slicing\n",
        "\n",
        "### One-dimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "6e082420"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a = np.arange(0, 11)\n",
        "a"
      ],
      "id": "3860cf58",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[0]"
      ],
      "id": "b6221e7a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-1]"
      ],
      "id": "20d41985",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[4]"
      ],
      "id": "2e3fb1a2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "c090633a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1]"
      ],
      "id": "d4839078",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1:2]"
      ],
      "id": "476da6a2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "58c23258"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[:5]"
      ],
      "id": "060f0d26",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-5:]"
      ],
      "id": "5fcc1449",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[::-2]"
      ],
      "id": "8f59a6c9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Multidimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "acf45e62"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = lambda m, n: n + 10*m"
      ],
      "id": "afd951e5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# please search for numpy.fromfunction at google\n",
        "A = np.fromfunction(f, (6, 6), dtype=int)\n",
        "A  "
      ],
      "id": "1fb7f92c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:, 1]  # the second column"
      ],
      "id": "a772a5e4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1, :]  # the second row"
      ],
      "id": "4c92a34b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:3, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "f9a63180",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[3:, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "3ebd558c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[::2, ::2]"
      ],
      "id": "37b88882",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1::2, 1::3]"
      ],
      "id": "13d76291",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Views\n",
        "\n",
        "* Subarrays that are extracted from arrays using slice operations are **alternative views** of the same underlying array data. That is, $~$they are arrays that refer to the same data in memory as the original array, $~$but with a different `strides` configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "* When elements in a view are assigned new values, $~$the values of the original\n",
        "array are therefore also updated. For example,\n"
      ],
      "id": "e010045a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[1:5, 1:5]\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "59830330",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[:, :] = 0\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "a9a03388",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* When a copy rather than a view is needed, the view can be copied explicitly by using the `copy` method of the `ndarray` instance\n"
      ],
      "id": "d21c6484"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C = B[1:3, 1:3].copy()\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "8db52c87",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C[:, :] = 1\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "dab1acfe",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "a46cf3e1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Fancy indexing and boolean-valued indexing\n"
      ],
      "id": "38a9c319"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.linspace(0, 1, 11)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "ada2e445",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[np.array([0, 2, 4])]"
      ],
      "id": "3d297739",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[[0, 2, 4]]"
      ],
      "id": "e7bde5c3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "750bd3a8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A > 0.5"
      ],
      "id": "c02bb62c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 0.5]"
      ],
      "id": "7c28c46f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* Unlike arrays created by using slices, $~$**the arrays returned using fancy indexing and Boolean-valued\n",
        "indexing are not views**, $~$but rather new independent arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "319c102e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)\n",
        "indices = [2, 4, 6]"
      ],
      "id": "84b3a803",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[indices]"
      ],
      "id": "6bf7543d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "6a2ff495",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[indices] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "4b85343e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "57f4472a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)"
      ],
      "id": "e8f888b0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[A > 5]"
      ],
      "id": "8407cd74",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "0eb4b7e0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 5] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "14d999de",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Summery\n"
      ],
      "id": "433601c4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, :')"
      ],
      "id": "d38c906a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0')"
      ],
      "id": "4b5a2e80",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1, :')"
      ],
      "id": "63fc2eed",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, 2')"
      ],
      "id": "7caac27b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "82e85423"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 0:2')"
      ],
      "id": "9a61065e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 2:4')"
      ],
      "id": "22775be7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '::2, ::2')"
      ],
      "id": "3daf3d16",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1::2, 1::2')"
      ],
      "id": "404b3971",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "201c4c8c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '[1, 3], [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "50725aa6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "8efa2744",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1:3, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "2bd50c60",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Reshaping and resizing\n",
        "\n",
        "* Reshaping an array does not require modifying the underlying array data; it only changes in how the data is interpreted, by redefining the array’s strides attribute\n"
      ],
      "id": "ef3c5e22"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.reshape(data, (1, 4))\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "0592c20c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0, 1] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "3a517ede",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.reshape(4)\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "c03bfcd2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[1] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "4906d0d1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "51625326"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.ravel(data)\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "8292c308",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "7a2a2a35",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* The `ndarray` method `flatten` perform the same function, $~$but\n",
        "returns a **copy** instead of a view\n"
      ],
      "id": "285650ac"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.flatten()\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "c3ebe314",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[0] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "c637c934",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "86ce315c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(0, 5)\n",
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "0444b2be",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column = data[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "column"
      ],
      "id": "74e50054",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column.shape"
      ],
      "id": "6b9d687d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row = data[np.newaxis, :]\n",
        "row"
      ],
      "id": "55771e04",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row.shape"
      ],
      "id": "d1e5e6da",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row[0, 0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "c8d3aa74",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
